         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne botanic &amp; zoolog. Garden, ¶ 24 October 1860. ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to bring under the favorable consideration of the City Council the desirability, that the foot-path around the ground...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">60.10.24b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Edmund FitzGibbon</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 56M, unit 822, VPRS 3181/P inwards correspondence registers, VA 511 Melbourne<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>City Council, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne botanic &amp; zoolog. Garden,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">24 October 1860.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to bring under the favorable consideration of the City Council the desirability, that the foot-path around the ground granted to the Royal Society may be raised, the present level being on most places considerably below that finally to be adopted.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have taken the liberty of soliciting the attention of the Municipality to this requirement, as the plantations on the ground of the society are severely suffering from the drying effect, caused as well by the rapid of flow of all humidity, as by the edges of the ground to a considerable depth being exposed to the parching influence of the sun.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Since moreover soil for raising the foot-path is at present obtainable from some excavations in the vicinity, I beg to solicit in the interest of the Royal Society the aid of the Municipality in carrying out the above improvements.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>No response to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the request has been found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your most obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The Town clerk &amp;c &amp;c &amp;c of Melbourne</p>
         </div>
      </body>
